@NODE MAIN "Historique"

@{fg highlight}@{B}@{U}Historique@{fg text}@{UB}@{UU}

@{B}7.1 (26.01.2002 12:39:54)@{UB}
    - Ajout de nouveux types d'outils :
      · NOSIZEABLE - la fenętre principale ne peut pas ętre redimensionnée.
      · NONAVBUTTS - N'affiche pas les boutons de navigation.
      · 3DLOOK     - Aspect 3D pour les boutons de navigation.
    - Possibilité d'assigner les scripts ARexx ŕ des champs de TEXTE.
      Les scripts seront appelés ŕ chaque rafraichissement de
      l'enregistrement.
    - Ajout des options : « Projet|Définir... » utilisées pour définir
      les champs.
    - Le menu « Editer|Marquer| » a été divisé en : « Editer|Marquer| » et
      « Editer|Démarquer| ».
    - Ajout des éléments de menu suivants :
      · "?|Aide..." - appel l'aide en ligne
      · "?|Raccourcis..." - appel l'aide en ligne
      · "?|courrier élec...." - ouvre le programme de courrier électronique
      · "Chercher|Aller|Marqué suivant" - se rend ŕ l'enregistrement marqué qui suit
      · "Chercher|Aller|Marqué précédent" - se rend ŕ l'enregistrement marqué précédent
      · "Chercher|Aller|Premier marqué" - se rend au premier enregistrement marqué
      · "Chercher|Aller|Dernier marqué" - se rend au dernier enregistrement marqué
      · "Chercher|Aller|Non-marqué suivant" - se rend ŕ l'enregistrement non-marqué qui suit
      · "Chercher|Aller|Non-marqué précédent" - se rend ŕ l'enregistrement non-marqué précédent
      · "Chercher|Aller|Premier non-marqué " - se rend au premier enregistrement non-marqué
      · "Chercher|Aller|Dernier non-marqué " - se rend au dernier enregistrement non-marqué
    - Ajout de l'aide en ligne disponible via la touche [ help ].
    - Nouveau menu contextuel de navigation associé aux gadgets de la fenętre.
    - Les gadgets « Restituer » et « Derničre sauvegarde » des réglages
      du programme ont été placé dans le menu contextuel.
    - Ajout de la possibilité de déplacer la barre d'outils, vous pouvez
      la déplacer en utilisant la fenętre des réglages ou les types d'outils.
    - Nouvelles options dans la fenętre des réglages, avec les types
      d'outils suivants : NOSIZEABLE, NONAVBUTTS.

@{B}7.0 (07.10.2001 12:53:45)@{UB}
    - Ajout de la documentation en anglais (merci ATO).
    - Ajout de quelques autres langues (merci ATO).
    - Changement du nom en XBaze.
    - Retrait des erreurs connues.
    - Reconstruction du menu (et ajout de nouvelles commandes).
    - Ajout de la possibilité de mouvement ŕ travers tous les champs
      éditable en utilisant la touche de tabulation.
    - Nouveaux raccourcis pour se déplacer ŕ travers les enregistrements.
    - Nouvelles commandes ARexx :
      · GUIFIND
      · GUISORT
      · BROWSE <field name>
      · ISDEFAULT
      · STATISTICS <field name>
      · CLEAR
      · RESET
      · DELUNMARKED
    - Ajout des boutons sur la fenętre pour les opérations sur les
      enregistrements.
    - Ajout des barres de défilement pour les fenętres.
    - Ajout du bouton d'information sur le projet sur la fenętre.
    - Optimisation des options de recherche.
    - Retrait des types d'outils NOHIGLABEL, NOBORDER et RXPORTNAME.
    - Changement de l'interface pour la « définition des champs »,
      « Recherche d'enregistrement », « Impression du projet » et réglages
      des fenętres.
    - Échange du gadget « Reset » par un menu contextuel.
    - Optimisation et ajout d'options.
    - Possibilité de stocker les programmes ARexx dans le volume « T: »
      pour gagner de la vitesse d'exécution.
    - Changement de sélection des champs pour les options de statistique
      (ajout du gadget dans la fenętre des statistiques).
    - Reconstruction des champs des menus contextuels.
    - D'autres modifications.

@{B}6.6 (22.06.2000 16:50:43)@{UB}
    - Changement des menus.
    - Ajout de nouveaux éléments de menus contextuels (support du
      presse-papiers).
    - Retrait d'erreurs connues.

@{B}6.5 (31.05.2000 11:56:09)@{UB}
    - Reorganized "Edit" menu.
    - Removed reading/writing program settings bugs.
    - Added possibility to specify number of  digits  after  comma  to
      statistics option.
    - Added possibility to save statistics in two formats.
    - Changed some english strings.
    - Adden 4 new commands "%".

@{B}6.4 (21.05.2000 15:32:17)@{UB}
    - Added possibilityy to edit "*" menu (you can add  new  entry  by
      selecting "..." item from this menu).
    - Added Italian catalog (author: Virginio Savani)

@{B}6.3 (15.05.2000 17:20:48)@{UB}
    - Fixed documentation.
    - Fixed printing option.
    - Removed known bugs.
    - Fixed GUI.
    - Added new shortcut to  "Find  record"  window:  [SHIFT]  [ENTER]
      working like "All..." option.
    - Changed menu.
    - New option in "Program setting" window -  "Use  screen  font  in
      requesters and child windows"
    - Added popupmenu for fields (press right mouse  button  over  the
      field in main or design window).
    - Added new option for "String" and "Amount" fields - URL address.
    - Updated Spanish catalog (author: Dámaso D. Estévez).

@{B}6.2 (28.04.2000 17:33:00)@{UB}
    - Fixed documentation.
    - Removed known bugs.
    - Changed some strings.
    - Changed GUI.
    - Fixed progress indicator.
    - Added new option to menu ("Project|New...").
    - Added possibility to give labels for fields.
    - Changes in "Text" field type.

@{B}6.1 (09.02.2000)@{UB}
    - Fixed documentation.
    - Changed some strings.
    - Removed known bugs.
    - Changed: fields names in "Filed  definition"  window,  names  of
      cycle gadget positions and list of predefined values don't  need
      <Enter> anymore.
    - Added possibility to set injected and rejected characters.
    - Added possibility to  set  number  of  lines  for  "String"  and
      "Amount" fields by mouse  dragging  borders  of  field  (like  a
      sizing field)
    - Changed menu in "Design" window.
    - Added new options in "Design" window: "Cut", "Copy" and "Paste".
    - Other changes.

@{B}6.0 (24.11.1999 15:54:06)@{UB}
    - Added ARexx port.
    - Updated documentation.
    - Added new appicon.
    - Added shortcuts:
      - [CONTROL] [CURSOR UP]/[CURSOR DOWN] - (for string  field  with
        predefined values) changes content of this field by predefined
        values from list
      - CTRL] [SHIFT] [<field shortcut>] - hides/shows field
      - [CTRL] [SHIFT] [<doubleclick close by field>] - hides field
      - [CTRL] [SHIFT] [ENTER] - shows all fields
    - Added new flag for field - "Saveable".  Default:  this  flag  is
      marked. Unmark this flag causes that content of field doesn't be
      saved, that means that content of this field doesn't change when
      user changes records. It's usefull for ARexx programs.
    - Changed menu in "Design" window.
    - Added possibility to load/save view from "Design" window.
    - Added possibility to edit "*" menu.
    - "About" window divided into two separate windows.
    - Optimized load view  option:  now  loads  only  information  for
      fields.
    - Added progress indicator (you can turn it off by  tooltypes  and
      program settings).
    - Added STARTICONIFIED tooltype, which  cause  that  XBaze  starts
      iconified.
    - Changed statistics window.
    - Optimized statistics option.
    - Changed strings in English and Polish locale files.
    - Removed known bugs.
    - Other changes.

@{B}5.6 (11.12.1998 14:15:31)@{UB}
    - Removed "No border" flag for "String" and "Amount" fields.
    - Added possibility to clone fields in "Design" window.
    - Added possibility to append project or  load  as  view  directly
      from "*" menu. If you want to append view please hold down [ALT]
      key, or hold down [CTRL] to append file to current project.
    - Some cosmetic changes.
    - Removed known bugs.

@{B}5.5 (23.11.1998 15:10:36)@{UB}
    - Optimized loading.
    - Added possiiblity to protect project with password.
    - Added variables to initial value for field.
    - Added new field type - "Text" - field for read only.
    - Added new field type -  "Button"  -  you  can  start  any  other
      programs, display pictures, etc.
    - Added default value for "String" field. Field will be filled  by
      this value when user doesn't fill this field and press  [ENTER].
      It's also possible to use variables like in initial values.
    - Statistics option moved to main menu.
    - Some cosmetic changes.
    - Removed known bugs.

@{B}4.5 (14.10.1998 14:13:28)@{UB}
    - Moved Export option from main menu to Print project window.
    - Changed "Project|Clear" and "Edit|Reset..."
    - Added menu from which you can select project to load.
    - Changed Find record window.
    - Added statistics option in Browse records window.
    - Added possibility to remember  creation  and  last  modification
      date.
    
@{B}4.0 (06.09.1998 14:46:55)@{UB}
    Added:
      - possibility to join projects
      - possibility to save and load views
      - possibility to delete project
      - possibility to change project name
      - [ALT] [ENTER] inserts to field content of field from  previous
        record
      - reload project option
      - some changes in menu.

@{B}3.2 (12.07.1998 15:08:26)@{UB}
    - Added popup gadget to  string/amount  fields,  from  which  user
      could select one of predefined values.
    - Added possibility  to  define  initial  values,  which  will  be
      inserted after adding new record. It's also possible  to  insert
      content from previous record.
    - Removed known bugs.
    - Changed save format. Program is still able to load from prevoius
      versions.
    - Updated Spanish catalog.

@{B}3.1 (03.07.1998 17:35:14)@{UB}
    - Fixed some bugs.
    - Added configurable printing option.
    - Added new feature in design window: when  you  drag  field  with
      pressed <SHIFT> key, after drop field  will  be  placed  in  new
      line.

@{B}3.0a (26.06.1998 10:52:17)@{UB}
    - Removed small bug.
    - Added Spanish catalog (thanks to Dámaso D. Estévez).

@{B}3.0 (25.06.1998 15:12:52)@{UB}
    - Removed possibility to edit label placement.
    - Removed bug with locale.library. On  Amigas  with  OS3.0  locale
      doesn't work, because program tried to open locale.library  v39+
      and WB3.0 has got v38 (reported by Krashan/BlaBla).
    - Added some changes sugested by Krasgan
    - Added support for markers  and  some  options  in  Record  menu.
      Marked records could be exported or deleted.
    - Added new flag in find record window,  which  could  automaticly
      mark all matched records.    
    - Some changes in browse window:
      · removed "Order" gadget
      · added menu to window
      · added to menu possibility to sort records
      · added possibility to show only marked records
      · added possibility to show only that records which was found by
        find option with set "Make list" flag.
    - Added possibility to drag&drop fields and their sizes in  design
      window.
    - Tab in design window now changed in separated window.
    - Added new fields types: BOOLEAN and CYCLE, realized by  CHECKBOX
      and CYCLE gadgets.
    - Added possibility to change settings from main program.  Program
      saves settings to icon tooltypes.
    - Added French catalog (thanks to Jerome Chesnot).
    - Now "Undo" function brings back record to the primary form.
    - Added multiline string gadget.

@{B}2.05 (28.02.1998 14:15:49)@{UB}
    - Added patterns to windows.
    - Added  new  position  to  "Order"  gadget  in  browse  window  -
      "Reverse" - all records  will  be  sorted  opposite  to  current
      records order.
    - Some small fixes.

@{B}2.0 (07.02.1998 22:45:10)@{UB}
    - Changed status to "CARDWARE". If you use  this  program,  please
      send to me postcard with your city.
    - Added possibility to specify placement of field name.
    - Added possibility to hide field name.
    - Added possibility to hide field border. 
    - Added new field type - "Amount" - content of this field will  be
      treated as number by sort option.
    - Replaced in find record window  two  cycle  gadgets  to  specify
      search direction and search range by one cycle gadget.
    - Some cosmetic changes.
    - Removed some bugs.
    - Added new  tooltype  -  NOHIGHLABEL  -  which  disable  globally
      HIGHLABEL mode for fields.
    - Added new menu  entry  "Operations/Show  all"  which  shows  all
      fields.
    - Added possibility to switch program to browse mode  by  pressing
      [AMIGA] + [SHIFT] + underscore letter.
    - Added Reset gadget to field definition window.
    - Added new flag "Make list" to the search window, which puts  all
      matched records into window similar to browse window.
    - Added design window  in  which  user  could  freely  locate  all
      fields.  
    - Added new tooltype - NOBORDER - which globally disables  borders
      for fields.
    - Added  new  flag  for  field  -  NOHIGHLABEL  -  which  disables
      HIGHLABEL mode for field.
    - Now program saves window position (sugested by Krashan/BlaBla).
    - Added new tooltype - IGNSAVEDWINPOS - which ignores saved window
      position.
    - Added possibility to select operator in find record window.

@{B}1.4 (28.11.1997 18:11:26)@{UB}
    - Changed field definition window.
    - Changed Polish catalog and English strings in program.
    - Changed save format.
    - Added possibility to specify separation character (TAB or comma)
      to export to ASCII file.
    - Added possibility to import ASCII files with comma as separation
      character.
    - Added browse mode (suggested by Tomash/BlaBla). Now you can  see
      one field of all records at one  time.  To  enable  browse  mode
      please   select   field  and  choose  "Operations/Browse..."  or
      doubleclick on the field. You can sorting and filtering  records
      freely.      
    - Added possibility to  fast  call  field  definition  window,  by
      doubleclick on field with  [SHIFT]  key,  and  field  attributes
      window by doubleclick with [ALT] key.
    - Removed limitation to 15 fields in record.
    - Added new tooltype - FONT=<font name/font size>
    - Some changes and fixes.

@{B}1.3 (20.10.1997 10:34:38)@{UB}
    - Added cursors support for LISTVIEW gadget.
    - Added new shortcut - [SHIFT] [ENTER] - activates last field.
    - Added new shortcut - [HELP] - information about field.
    - Some little fixes.
    - Moved and renamed "Repeat data" flag, now  it  is  in  "Options"
      window and named "Repeatedly data entering".
    - Removed "Append..."  and "Jump to..." options.
    - Added Appicon.
    - Added iconify option (suggested by Tomash/BlaBla).
    - Added possibility to localize shortcuts.
    - Changed save format, much more faster. Now program does not save
      data as ASCII by default, but in new format. But is  still  able
      to load/save ASCII files.
    - Removed support for reqtools.library  requesters  (suggested  by
      Tomash/BlaBla), now  using  asl.library.  If  you  want  to  use
      ReqTools requesters please use ReqToolsPatch or MCP.
    - Rearraged field definition window, now much more comfortable  in
      use.
 
@{B}1.2 (21.09.1997 20:21:24)@{UB}
    - Now program requires AmigaOS3+
    - Added case sensitive flag to search option.
    - Added possibility to set searching record  range  and  searching
      direction (normal or reverse).
    - Added shortcuts to all gadgets in windows.
    - Added definable shortcuts for fields.
    - Added possibility to  insert  space  after  field  ("Add  space"
      flag).
    - Added new flag - Repeat data - if this flag is set, and in empty
      field you press [RETURN] value  from  previous  record  will  be
      placed into current field.
    - Added possibility to hide fields.
    - Changed GUI in field definition window.
    - Fixed sorting  option.  If  you  sort  already  sorted  project,
      project doesn't change its state to "changed".
    - Added separated requesters to confirm: clear, load and quit.
    - Changed XBF save format.
    - Added possibility to remember windows sizes and positions.
    - Debugged with help of Mungwall and Enforcer.
 
@{B}0.7 (16.08.1997 19:10:43)@{UB}
    - Added possibility to sort using Polish order  without  installed
      Polish locale  (tooltype  LOCALESORT  must  be  disabled).  It's
      usefull for Polish users without Polish locale package.
    - Optimized sorting option.

@{B}0.6 (15.08.1997 godz. 13:01:12)@{UB}
    - Fixed field definition options. Now if you add  new  fields  and
      remove it  without  closing  field  definition  window,  program
      doesn't change project state to "changed".
    - Replaced shortcut to "Project|Clear|Project..." option from  "R"
      to "L".
    - Changed actual record display format.
    - Some little changes.

@{B}0.430 (17.07.1997 23:27:38)@{UB}
    - Replaced "Project|New..." option with "Project|Clear|Project..."
      and "Project|Clear|Data...".
    - Removed SIZEGADGET tooltype.
    - Removed unused gadgets from field definition window.
    - Added gadget to specify field size in field definition window.
    - Replaced slider for field size by INTEGER gadget.
    - Added option to join projects.
    - Added icons for program and projects.

@{B}0.420 (01.07.1997)@{UB}
    - First public version.

@ENDNODE

